Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在實習和筆試不及格的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.32,0:00:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有因不得已理由而缺席的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及蹺實習課而且連補課\N都想開溜卻被我活逮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到家政科料理實習
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國高中部聯合舉辦的\N夏季特別補修課程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為三田村老師突然生病請假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在活動研究會\N全面協助之下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的補課\N就由我杉浦碧來主持
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家準備有所覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼跟什麼呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的心情 飛散灑滿其中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果命中註定的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠是你那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現實卻無法如願以償
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在閃耀光芒的風裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想的羽毛 飄然落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣邁向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.35,0:01:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就這麼美麗地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始奔騰的熱烈心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍動出跟那一天同樣的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.73,0:02:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你率直的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永遠看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來\N大家要準備挑戰烹飪工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第10話 蛋糕大戰!!!!\N我們邀請到了特別講師\N來參與本次補課
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧!特別來賓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要扯到我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…杉浦老師，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請指導迷惘的學生吧，修女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二三，謝謝妳的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平常沒什麼機會跟學生接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次真的很開心喔 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而擔任評審的是\N所有女生憧憬的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人稱"黎人學長"的學生會副會長\N以及副會長的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外還有剛好路過\N十分幸運的兩位男老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎人學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～真令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實在很想開溜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對戰的形式是以公平公正的抽籤\N而決定出來的三人團體賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了發表本次主題的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要各位挑戰的主題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要使用這裡準備的材料\N不管做哪種蛋糕都OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼第一屆風華盃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"製作充滿愛情的蛋糕"\N"真正的廚師是我"爭霸戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會扯太遠了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣學姐，加油呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓住男人的心\N一定要先抓住男人的胃喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕，有蛋糕可以吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要自己動手做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一定要在今天\N自己動手做蛋糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶，你起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛\N進來之前應該先敲門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶，你喜歡甜食嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要開始了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實在的\N我還真的蠻想去那裡瞧瞧耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就今天不行喔，對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家政補課是做蛋糕啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣也要做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣的蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸酸甜甜的蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想吃舞衣做的蛋糕啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她一定不會讓我吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好想吃吃看耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆來搗蛋吧，你說呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為迎接下一個黃金時代來臨…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做什麼蛋糕呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白小姐喜歡\N用大吉嶺紅茶做的戚風蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦\N我不是在問妳理事長的喜好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅茶戚風!我也很喜歡!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優同學，妳呢？有沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戚風蛋糕的作法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一，首先將雞蛋的\N蛋白和蛋黃分開，蛋黃放進碗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK，就做戚風蛋糕吧…\N然後快速的攪拌讓它發泡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙哈蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想做巧克力蛋糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能是廉價蛋糕!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙哈蛋糕可是澳大利亞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧地利啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澳大利…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧地利的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈布…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈布士…堡王家的\N法蘭…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭茲 ． 約瑟夫一世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之\N是很偉大的人吃的巧克力蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我負責指揮!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一切就有勞妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會啦\N會長妳就在一旁喝茶納涼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到我竟然得\N跟妳這種生活糜爛傢伙搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個只會收集內褲的\N寂寞女人沒有資格說我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打架？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是給予我的考驗嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃蛋糕的話，去買不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真是吃飽太閒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，反正做好會請我吃的話\N不幫忙也說不過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼要做蛋糕啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我講了你一定會笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然一定會覺得被我打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說啦你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實啊，今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，好好，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做什麼好？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那換我來攪拌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優同學，打泡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正要開始攪拌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有有有!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個很麻煩吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攪拌完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我泡好紅茶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很燙，請務必小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像個白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連個蛋都不會打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來妳好像也只有\N跟男人糾纏不清的能力而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起妳這個缺乏男人滋潤\N女性荷爾蒙變的像豬油一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是健康多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我挖出妳的大腦來看看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後直接拿來\N當海綿蛋糕用怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯然把妳的寬額頭切開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會比打蛋有趣多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來幫妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了妳!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳們兩個住手啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠洲城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力得用\N隔水加熱方式來融化耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔水？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:09:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要當心背後會被偷襲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正快點做好，就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女，接下來該做什麼好？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禱…禱告吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳給我差不多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就亂七八糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底我們會吃到什麼東西啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她們用心製作出來的\N不管怎樣一定都會很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我只是假設一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會對那個粗魯女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她之間的事情\N和你有什麼關係呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人難過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說你真的很孝順姊姊\N還是什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小我就一直給她添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她所為我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不只是這點小事\N可以報答的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，那我來做個收尾…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要說要買做糖霜用的細砂糖\N這樣就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶，不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒差啦，你去顧好蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去去就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了!到了最後收尾的時刻啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生奇蹟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有禱告啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.86,0:12:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著該做什麼好？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主如是說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每100公克鮮奶油\N要摻入神聖數量的10公克砂糖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂糖嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命，在底下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙，蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在五秒鐘內撿起來\N都還可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命，妳在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位，請保護蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是身為一名女傭應該做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點啊，命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無依者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙，把我的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩個等等啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫妳們等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校裡面怎麼可以這樣!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉唆!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了做出那個蛋糕\N你知道我們花了多少功夫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（因淨化槽整修中，禁止使用）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡，包夾牠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下奶油而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為還可以逃得掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的蛋糕還來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞…搞得補課的時候一陣慌亂…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦具土!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，這是要給姊姊的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的惡行到此為止!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的臭怪物!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝填銀彈!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦具土，上!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，妳又搞什麼笨把戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不關我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親，我要違背你的教誨了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源內
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推參!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必殺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地獄釜!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:17:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是，我不是尾久崎晶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身負自怪物手中\N守護校園使命的神秘忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都是你在守護我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的忍者先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事別告訴任何人，知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，晶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然跟計畫有所出入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過狀況變有趣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大意了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又長大了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙，還沒察覺到吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請試吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，你不能死!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便咒我死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳最好有所覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事妳的責任可大了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們到底做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了，快開門啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想快點沖個澡!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是糟透了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，生日快樂!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃!好好吃喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我跟晶拼命做出來的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是啊，晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？不好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃，很好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海，謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為舞衣妳都沒跟我們說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是巧海來找我們商量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們根本還不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為覺得這樣\N好像在暗示什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這種見外的話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，這是我們的一點心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好想要這個耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:20:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，那我幫妳按摩肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，很癢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣真是性感啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是最棒的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然發生很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我覺得能來這間學校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖我夏姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美袋命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上三人是女武神，對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們打敗了我們的無依者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要將那三人處理掉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只要監視她們的行動就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來就已經四個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要儘快找出剩餘的女武神…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.26,0:22:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出HiME，並確認身份
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，父親
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.94,0:22:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請別迷惘」 這句話\N我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.68,0:22:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有無法傳達給你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過寂寞的笑容搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫過傷口 Lonely good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連熱情都會讓我痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著永恆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.41,0:22:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是我的天空我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那段燃燒熔化的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:23:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記 要時時想起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是收藏在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.20,0:23:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Search for my life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天還會再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜歡你那清澈的雙眼 現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上各自的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新開始前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,0:23:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光與闇的圓舞曲\N不…不好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.37,0:23:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光與闇的圓舞曲\N武田，別慌張，發生什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.23,0:23:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有女孩子裸體…躺在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.94,0:23:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武田，你到底幹了什麼好事!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.84,0:23:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春的衝動讓我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.94,0:23:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:24:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛認識的時候，會覺得\N"這女生在搞什麼啊？"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是在大學的新訓課程\N剛好坐在我隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.68,0:24:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就很厚臉皮地拼命找我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.81,0:24:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，當我察覺到的時候\N我已經跟著她的步調走了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.82,0:24:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看起來傻傻的\N但實際上卻不是那樣一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.85,0:24:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，你相信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.12,0:24:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看她那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.62,0:24:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在文學系可是公認的才女喔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許也因為她很喜歡考古研究
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.76,0:24:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此比較喜歡年長男性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.83,0:24:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對有趣的事情\N她都喜歡湊熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.44,0:24:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣，我也常會被拖下水
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.47,0:24:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，很奇妙的是\N我並不會很討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.91,0:24:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對，說真的\N還真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.95,0:24:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有碧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.45,0:24:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的大學生活才能這麼充實
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.22,0:24:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點我很感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.56,0:24:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.72,0:24:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份孽緣\N竟然可以維持這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.93,0:24:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不禁還是令人想嘆口氣啊


